\n<br />\n「你唔應該係到出現，你會有危險！」馬面大呼。<br />\n<br />\n平常冷靜無比的馬面竟然會方寸大亂。<br />\n<br />\n「危險？」我還未接受出賣我的馬面對我所說的勸戒。<br />\n<br />\n「係我。」華哥緩緩步上二樓，站在馬面親弟身旁。<br />\n<br />\n「我一直覺得你有古怪，估唔到你......」馬面怒目相視。<br />\n<br />\n此時此刻，我明白了馬面的苦衷，亦知道眼前除了馬面之外，全都是敵人。<br />\n<br />\n「由一開始，你地全部人都係我既棋子......唔係，係玩具先岩。」他又吃了一塊巧克力。<br />\n<br />\n「牛奶朱古力，真到呢一刻，我先感受到咩叫甜，咩叫快樂。」<br />\n<br />\n「睇住你班廢柴出賣朋友，呢種人生一大樂事仲可以去邊到搵？」"},{"pid":"ce55d160632b476062be5efd4f9e6877c701d309","tid":290007,"uid":2095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:33:33.000Z","msg":"推下新post先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a4411f2d955f24d82c5425aba9e1c7dd1f5e9d","tid":290007,"uid":46742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:47:38.000Z","msg":"食死個馬面細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb06abf8b51cbf8f96511ce4694e7f4016da29c","tid":290007,"uid":101701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:52:14.000Z","msg":"臭閪"},{"pid":"1258dbd2724b698059b00247925b85c9dfb0ea76","tid":290007,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:05:00.000Z","msg":"人黎捉文怡做十世妓女<br />\n華哥做十世惡霸<br />\n馬面細佬做十世乞衣<br />\n<br />\n等十世之後牛頭做左降龍先黎救佢地！"},{"pid":"83e0ee54ad1c3b9052e86b60347e7ac41dfe3d64","tid":290007,"uid":65956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:10:57.000Z","msg":"牛頭俾女fake完開無雙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1762b2174101ed2ea58186b456c7cffa5d6f2bdd","tid":290007,"uid":18318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:25:20.000Z","msg":"皮已正"},{"pid":"fce692f889ceb47d9f07c9bc405d2dbb21976090","tid":290007,"uid":27680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:31:13.000Z","msg":"臭雞！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14deb4f829eb4214362646d61362b11d51e8b146","tid":290007,"uid":86684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:40:23.000Z","msg":"他把手指指向我與馬面。<br />\n<br />\n「廢話少講，我應承你既野已經做好，你要守信用。」馬面對廢柴二字，感覺不大。<br />\n<br />\n「哥哥，你一世人都係咁忠直，但估唔到今次你會感情用事。」他從口袋中掏出手機。<br />\n<br />\n「感情用事既人，只有一個下場，就係失敗。」<br />\n<br />\n「你要記住任何人都只係數字，一個幫你追求成功，享樂既工具。」<br />\n<br />\n「正如私家車既作用係代步，但一旦出現問題，佢既下場就只有報廢，絕對唔可以被拖累。」<br />\n<br />\n他的指尖在螢幕上遊走。<br />\n<br />\n「救命啊！救命啊！」螢幕傳來呼天搶地的哭泣聲。<br />\n<br />\n「今次，我要你輸得一敗塗地，永不翻生。」"},{"pid":"4a837b5475e72da9cbf66cfecede3b1b71ad69c6","tid":290007,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:44:01.000Z","msg":"如果太多牛奶味"},{"pid":"2eb27fbb005fc0ff4969e30786a3bc506984628d","tid":290007,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d5eb5725d92968b3860e2b95dc82820a5d4114","tid":290007,"uid":74096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:50:52.000Z","msg":"唔好爛尾收場呀"},{"pid":"40efaf25f1470bcc436d459811baa1ac064e7d88","tid":290007,"uid":32175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T16:22:45.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"cd66b606eccaf4fb5b9ebe8711ed040a951ca9ef","tid":290007,"uid":27680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T16:29:19.000Z","msg":"仲未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd60e797d882502d72fef7abd2612946ab4d2650","tid":290007,"uid":59887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T16:46:37.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3edb2f90dafa6d17f924a5f08a1ef21a3df48ec","tid":290007,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T16:57:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係味我睇小左野？</blockquote><br />\n葡提子巴打嘅意思係咪指上個post最後一篇<br />\n同呢個post第一篇中間好似少咗啲嘢咁<img src=\"/a