.....<br />\n<br />\n她是一個好女孩，我的好妻子，雖然我對她沒有感情，但最少有感激。"},{"pid":"61308bd4acbeff3e2291da50fbb2a52e607b823d","tid":290007,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實無灰飛煙滅</blockquote><br />\n咁o係咪會一世係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五陰會滅 但心識不滅"},{"pid":"f03d874c1cb6f8fad133ec999b27ff1d3796d467","tid":290007,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:22:19.000Z","msg":"徳仔同婆婆唔係已經食左毒藥自殺左咩？點解仲會俾馬面細佬捉住？"},{"pid":"d2a500f67c42b01c3a1b6bf7d5f17c3ad167c2b0","tid":290007,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:29:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>徳仔同<del>婆婆</del>嫲嫲唔係已經食左毒藥自殺左咩？點解仲會俾馬面細佬捉住？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a73ef18b16f680348dff227baa538697c587985d","tid":290007,"uid":92646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:29:34.000Z","msg":"點解我睇到咁迷惘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0bc278fc6cdeb5e80bdade0bbe30eaaa98f3ed0","tid":290007,"uid":33387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:32:00.000Z","msg":"搞唔掂喎 <br />\n寧願你慢慢寫 唔洗急 <br />\n講真<br />\n都追咗咁耐 唔爭在"}]}